Description:
You enter a nearby water mill, it seems empty at first glance, but then you hear a whisper directed at you.

"Sss...  you aren't my preys... sss...  you are scaring them... leave please.

But first, I have an offer for you… sss… if you happen to find a very strong venom and give it to me... sss... I will join your group after I finish this job."
DescriptionAction: You can't see who it is, but the offer seems interesting.
